metadata.name: Tiny World
metadata.description:
Tiny World - Delusions of Grandeur

We imagined a world that grows and shrinks according to our perceptions.

How unknown and big the world was when we were  a child.

How it got smaller as we got older.

Your experiences, perceptions, subconscious and ego shaped the world.

_

Created and Post in Adobe Photoshop

Technique _ Digital Painting, Photo Manipulation and Digital Collage

Format _ 5000 x 5000 pixel, JPEG
